txt.en: Your continued efforts to support An Shêru earns you greater favour with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Kindred with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
You must earn Kindred standing with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
You have done much for the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh and they now feel a kinship with you.
